headline: LKQ Corp. price target lowered to $43 from $46 at Roth Capital
summary: Roth Capital lowered the firm’s price target on LKQ Corp. (LKQ) to $43 from $46 but keeps a Buy rating on the shares after its Q3 earnings beat. Following outsized Q3 performance aided by a one-time tax benefit and the modest increasing of FY25 guidance, the firm maintains its net constructive stance on shares, the analyst tells investors in a research note.
